</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>DJI Mini 3 Pro 登場      香港價錢 + 詳細規格</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/11/dji-mini-3-pro/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=dji-mini-3-pro</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 11 May 2022 11:14:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍]]></category><category><![CDATA[dji]]></category><category><![CDATA[DJI mini 3 Pro]]></category><category><![CDATA[航拍機]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099244</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>DJI 於今日正式推出新一代 DJI Mini 3 Pro。DJI Mini 3 Pro 集輕小便攜、影像實力 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>DJI 於今日正式推出新一代 DJI Mini 3 Pro。DJI Mini 3 Pro 集輕小便攜、影像實力、避障系統、智慧功能於一身。DJI Mini 3 Pro 重量低於 249 克，延續小身形，高性能設計，搭載 1/1.3 英寸感測器，具三向環境感知能力，最長續航時間可達 47 分鐘。DJI Mini 3 Pro 創新構型在動力、避障、雲臺方面經過全新佈局，機身新增減阻設計並增大漿葉面積，大幅提升動力效能；首次前置後視避障感測器，並擴大了障礙物感知範圍，提升飛行安全體驗；雲臺經過全新規劃，可設置無損豎拍、大角度仰拍，令創作更有可塑性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08380-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ DJI Mini 3 Pro</p><p>延續前代低於 249 克的重量，DJI Mini 3 Pro 機臂摺疊方式和機身結構均經過重新設計，方便用家收納和出行輕鬆便捷。</p><h2>可達 47 分鐘續航力</h2><p>續航性能作為航拍創作的基礎，在消費級無人機中首次突破至最長 47 分鐘。全新構型設計通過改變機身傾角和增大槳葉面積，降低了風阻從而大幅提升動力效能，令 DJI Mini 3 Pro 的續航得到顯著突破。用家結合智豐飛行電池可使用長達 34 分鐘，選配長續航電池更可使用長達 47 分鐘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099272 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08340-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新設計改變機身傾角</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099275 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08373-2.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲增大槳葉面積</p><h2>三向避障性能</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 具三向避障性能，是 DJI Mini 系列迄今安全性最強的無人機。其配備前視、後視、下視雙目視覺感應系統和 ToF （Time-of-Flight），得益於創新構型，障礙物感知範圍大幅提升。在此基礎上，APAS 4.0 幫助下，更好的自主路徑規劃及靈敏避障，可自動探測並躲避飛行路徑中的障礙物，在複雜場景下也能順滑飛行。</p><h2><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099277 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08306-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099278 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08352-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲首次前置後視避障感測器</p><h2>12 公里最遠傳輸距離</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 採用 DJI O3 旗艦數位圖傳。DJI Mini 3 Pro 可設置 1080p/30fps 最高實時圖傳畫質和 12 公里最遠傳輸距離，最大圖傳碼率 18Mbps，且抗幹擾能力大幅增強，進一步提升複雜拍攝場景中的圖傳可靠性。DJI Mini 3 Pro 身形雖小，其動力冗餘設計帶來最高可抗 5 級風。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099282 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08354-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 12 公里最遠傳輸距離</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099281 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08350-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可抗 5 級風</p><h2>1/1.3 英寸感測器加大光圈</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 在影像系統上進行了專業升級，搭載 1/1.3 英寸影像感測器，新增雙原生 ISO，支援直出 HDR 影像，更高的動態範圍令明暗部位細節得以保留。DJI Mini 3 Pro 配備了 f/1.7 大光圈鏡頭，配合感光能力 2.44μm 四合一大像素，帶來純凈透亮的夜景效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099285 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08305-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備 f/1.7 大光圈鏡頭</p><h2>可錄製 4K/60fps 4800 萬像素 RAW 照片</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 最高可錄製 4K/60fps 影片和拍攝 4800 萬像素 RAW 格式照片。DJI Mini 3 Pro 支援 1080p/120fps 慢動作攝影，還新增 D-Cinelike 色彩模式，為創作者提供更廣闊的調整空間。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099299 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08365-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最高可錄製 4K/60fps 影片和拍攝 4800 萬像素 RAW 格式照片</p><h2>更多拍攝模式</h2><p>DJI Mini 3 Pro 首次設置無損豎拍和大角度仰拍，帶來豐富的視覺效果和多樣玩法，讓使用者更輕鬆拍攝大片。 得益於全新雲臺構型設計，DJI Mini 3 Pro 雲臺轉動限位更小，不僅能實現大角度仰拍，更支援無裁切豎拍，引領社交平臺航拍創意潮流。 DJI Mini 3 Pro 還支援焦點跟隨功能，配備智慧跟隨、聚焦、興趣點環繞三種跟拍模式，將主角始終鎖定在 C 位。大師鏡頭、延時攝影功能首次在 Mini 系列出現，讓航拍機自主完成複雜運鏡， 極大降低使用者創作門檻 。 使用者還可拍攝 180°、廣角、豎拍、球形全景照片。 此外，為提升使用者分享體驗，手機快傳功能支援 Wi-Fi 高速下載，最高速率可達 30MB/s。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099286 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08358-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無損豎拍</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099288 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08355-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無損豎拍</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099287 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-2048x1366.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08359-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大角度仰拍</p><h2><strong>豐富新增配件為創作加碼</strong></h2><p>DJI 推出專為 DJI Mini 3 Pro 設計的全新輕量化帶屏遙控器 DJI RC ，內置 DJI Fly app，操作便捷高效，告別繁瑣連接，大幅提升起飛效率。 專用帶屏遙控器讓使用者無需擔心手機電量，更能專注創作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099290 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08321-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新輕量化帶屏遙控器 DJI RC</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099293 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08308-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099291 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/KAN08360-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1099292 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-